Perfect Grade

Perfect Grade (PG) kits are the ultimate Gunpla experience, offering unmatched detail, advanced engineering, and premium quality at 1/60 scale. These kits feature intricate internal frames, realistic articulation, and optional LED lighting for select models. Explore our entire selection to see just how far the engineering has come since the line's inception in 1998!
